0.4.1 / 2014-12-11

* Bug fixes

  * Properly require 'active_support' before any of its modules

0.4.0 / 2012-09-07

* Breaking changes

  * You have to include activesupport in your Gemfile if you use the default cache store

* Enhancements

  * Remove dependency on ActiveSupport (unless you want the default cache store)

* Bug fixes

  * Properly handle redis forking

0.3.3 / 2012-04-17

* Enhancements

  * Test on MRI 1.8, MRI 1.9, and JRuby 1.6.7+

* Bug fixes

  * Fix Redis support. Tests were silently failing, made them loud and then fixed 'em.

0.3.2 / 2012-04-11

* Enhancements

  * Compatibility with Rails 3.2.x that uses ActiveSupport::Cache::FileStore

0.3.1 / 2012-04-10

* Bug fixes

  * Compatibility with Rails 2.x that calls Rails.cache.logger=
